name: Haibara Ai anime Style
description:
I made a doujin style LORA for Haibara Ai before,Now I trained one with the current anime style.

The style change made her too short in the anime, so that the AI ​​couldn't generate the same style of clothing, even though I used larger size screenshots.

So please use "anime screencap" to generate clothes with the same style

Added "breasts" to negative words to make sure she doesn't turn into Miyano Shiho,unless that's what you want.

By the way, sorry for Google Translate.
